{
  "stem": "15686.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because all I literally had with me was the clothes on my back and a little backpack that had a mess kit in it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, I think, a change of underwear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Other than that, there was-- [LAUGHS] we had no luggage and no belongings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we stayed in Casablanca about three days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they let us go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this is important, because it added three days to our itinerary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we got out of Casablanca and were heading for New York.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we got another four or five days, when one very early morning at dawn, we heard gunfire from a cannon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Again, we ran on deck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was this warship flying a British flag.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was a British destroyer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was, again, the same story. 'Yes, you're a neutral ship, and we mean you no harm, but you have Germans on board.' We-- [LAUGHS] we were the threat to the Allies!",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Poor kids! 'And we have to escort you to the nearest Allied port,' which happened to be Hamilton Bermuda.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the poor limped into Bermuda.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by this time, we were 15 days out of Lisbon, and we had no food, or water, or anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it was-- the last three days there was really rough.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Bermuda, they-- they gave us some food and things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the British went through the same routine as the Germans and Vichy French did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wanted to know, where do you come from?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where are you going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What did you do in France?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where were you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Do you have pictures?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Do you, you know-- they were looking for spies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they let us go after about two days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So in all, the journey took about three weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
